The package tts-cpp provides CMake integration:

  find_package(tts-cpp CONFIG REQUIRED)
  target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE tts-cpp::tts-cpp)

The following public headers are available:
  #include <tts-cpp/tts-cpp.h>                         // generic CLI entry point
  #include <tts-cpp/chatterbox/engine.h>               // persistent Engine API
  #include <tts-cpp/chatterbox/s3gen_pipeline.h>       // Chatterbox S3Gen + HiFT back-half

GPU backends are controlled by vcpkg features (ggml is vendored and
installed alongside tts-cpp):
  metal  - Metal GPU backend  (default-on for macOS/iOS)
  vulkan - Vulkan GPU backend (default-on for windows/linux/android)
